      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for optimized valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivers power to a GKN variable M-differential, ensuring precise torque distribution and mechanical grip. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains sharp with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is superlative, offering a visceral, high-revving driving experience without the collector-grade markup.",
